  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">To communicate with you, to send you information about our products, services, contests, and promotions, and to send offers to selected groups of customers on behalf of other businesses. When we send you offer on behalf of other businesses, we never give that business your name and address. If you do not wish to receive such offers, please let us know, and we will place you on a "do not contact" list.</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

