<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#fe94b180cc47443a96c767a:SecurityMechanism">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#SecurityMechanism"/>
  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">fe94b180cc47443a96c767a</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">What is phishing - Phishing is a scam where fraudsters pretend that they represent well-known companies to steal your personal information If you receive an email claiming to be from Hat World that asks you for your personal information do not respond We will never request your password user name credit card information or other personal information through email</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

