  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Your California Privacy Rights California Civil Code Section 1798 83 permits customers of Hat World who are California residents to request certain information regarding our disclosure of personal information to third parties for their direct marketing purposes To make such a request please click here to reach our Privacy Officer</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

